# Testing (Vitest)

## Placement

- **Unit / integration**: co-locate `*.test.ts` or `*.spec.ts` next to the module under test (`src/foo.test.ts` beside `src/foo.ts`).
- **End-to-end**: only under `tests/e2e/` at the workspace or app root (not beside individual components).

## Style

- Prefer small, deterministic tests; mock IO at repository boundaries when testing services.
- Use `describe` / `it` blocks that read like behavior specs; avoid testing implementation details.

## Workers

- Use Miniflare / `@cloudflare/vitest-pool-workers` patterns when you add Worker tests (not included in the minimal template).
